@startuml
title StayFinder - Container Diagram
left to right direction
skinparam rectangleStyle rounded

package "Client Layer" {
  rectangle "Mobile App\n(Expo + React Native)" as Mobile
}

package "Application Layer" {
  rectangle "REST API\n(Node.js + Express)" as Api
}

package "Data Layer" {
  database "Postgres\n(Supabase)" as Pg
}

package "AI/Data Pipeline Layer" {
  rectangle "Crawler Scripts\n(Python)" as Crawler
  rectangle "Import Script\n(Python)" as Importer
  rectangle "RAG Script\n(Chunk/Embed/Query)" as RagScript
}

Mobile --> Api : HTTP requests
Api --> Pg : Read/Write data
Api --> RagScript : AI query/summary
RagScript --> Pg : Chunks + cache\nretrieval
Crawler --> Importer : Raw/Compact files
Importer --> Pg : Upsert batch data

@enduml
